<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Mar1925"><font color="red">13 March 1925</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Ernest Walsh, dictated): When [the <i>Criterion</i> piece] appears (July next) I shall send you something and if you wish you may use my name as that of a future contributor &hellip; I have to return to the clinic in  a week in order to undergo another but less serious operation, after which I hope I shall be able to work with more ease. At present I am unable to read or write. </div>
